   		Our Software Engineers / Developers participate in the
   		specification, design, and implementation of client software
   		solutions. You will work with the team to evaluate candidate
   		technologies and approaches, and have significant autonomy
   		and responsibility to implement the solution. As a developer,
   		the following characteristics are desired:

   <ul class="listText">
		<li>Have a passion for software.  Nevo’s staff members love the
			intricacies and capabilities of the technologies we use.
		</li><li>Enjoy working smarter, finding elegant and effective
				 solutions to problems.
		</li><li>Be able to work both independently, and to function as
				 an integral member of team.  The Nevo atmosphere is highly
				 collegial and supportive.  We rely on each member of the team
				 to produce results, and to support each other.
		</li><li>Commit to creating high business value software using iterative,
				 collaborative, quality driven approaches.
		</li><li>Produce high quality, tested code that realizes the requirements
				 of the business application.  This comes not only from technical
				 skills but also from a commitment to quality and process.
   </ul>

<p>Most of our developers work at all layers of the application architecture,
from UI design to the persistence tier.  We believe strongly in effective processes
and value a deep knowledge of software engineering principles.


